# =============================================================================
# CONTRAINDICATIONS & WARNINGS
# =============================================================================
WARNINGS:
  - Do not use aggressive repair during critical operations
  - Always maintain backup before deep repairs
  - Human review required for structural changes
  - Isolate repair operations from production traffic
  - Monitor for repair-induced regressions

